title: El dia divertido de Falafel
description: Cuando Falafel decide empacar sus cosas e ir a la ciudad, Manzana y Cebollín deben convencerlo de quedarse.

title: La Suciedad
description: A Ben le encargan la tarea de limpiar la Chatarra, pero cuando, engañado por los viles villanos Fly Guys, permite que se lo roben, debe perseguirlos antes de que fabriquen una larva monstruosa imparable con un objetivo claro: destruir Las Vegas.

title: Be Afraid of the Dark
description: Ben travels into space to thwart Ghostfreak's diabolical plans. But is he hero enough to take on the Mummy, Werewolf and Frankenstein?

title: The Explorer's Club
description: The ninja must break into the Explorer's Club to obtain the second Scroll of Forbidden Spinjitzu, running afoul of the club's manager and irate club-members.

title: #LosConejosMágicos
description: Cuando Zee le pide a Kara que cuide a sus dos conejitos mágicos, pronto comienzan a multiplicarse y a desatar el caos por toda Metrópolis.
originalseriesname: DC Super Hero Girls en Espanol

title: Toma 10
description: Mientras Ben intenta rodar su propia película independiente, por accidente libera a una pandilla de insectos y, cuando la lucha se traslada a su guarida oculta, Ben debe enfrentarse a su líder narcisista: La Hormiga Reina.

title: Babysitting Bedlam/Rubbed the Wrong Way
description: Rubbed the Wrong Way: After a Bakugan field errupts the town kids stampede to get their own Bakugan but when the field is contaminated Lia must save the day./Babysitting Bedlam: Dan and Wynton meet a strange boy who leads them into an underground maze where they discover the boy's Bakugan has been enslaved.

title: Bored to Be Wild
description: Mega Man teams up with his crush, Ashley Adderley, to solve a series of science riddles left by Chemical Man, who's plotting to turn all the city's metal into rubber.

title: Hoyo En 10
description: Mientras Ben juega al minigolf, lo atacan los Ground Hawgs, una pandilla de mutantes convertidos en ciclistas del Doctor Ánimo. Pero cuando los Hawgs se dan cuenta de que la falsa aldea de minigolf no es un lugar real, Ben debe transformarse en alienígena para detenerlos antes de que elijan la ciudad verdadera que está a pocos metros de allí como su blanco.

title: Haunted Campfire
description: The campers must battle ghosts of their own creation after their scary stories mysteriously come true.

title: It Grows
description: As everyone celebrates Valentino for growing his first facial hair, a jealous Vic resorts to magical methods to grow a mustache and compete for attention.

title: Campfire Stories
description: The Titans are having a terrible time on their camping trip so Robin suggests that they each tell a scary campfire story.

title: Bakuzoned!/The Golden Secret
description: Bakuzoned!: Strata's return is much more than a simple rematch when he's been infected by a strange ooze and the AO are in danger of the same fate./The Golden Secret: Using Strata's gauntlet, the AO think they've found a way through the labyrinth, but soon discover trusting the enemy is not always best.

title: Itch to Explore
description: Craig's quest to map the entire Creek takes him and his friends into the treacherous Poison Ivy Grove.

title: The Dynamo Dynamic
description: Axel finds himself at the center of a disagreement between Sarge and Masko over what's more important in battle - the weapon or the one who wields it - after Dynamo bonds the trio together!

title: Parley Part 1
description: Megatron and Optimus parley in an attempt to unite against Starscream.

title: Saving Faith
description: Lloyd and his team plot to take control of the Oni Titan. Meanwhile in the First Realm, the Ninja fall into Iron Baron's clutches and an old master returns.

title: Shhh!
description: While chilling at a monastery with a no-noise policy, Ben can't keep quiet and accidentally awakens a dangerous Dragon hidden in a secret chamber below the hallowed halls. A job that might be too much for even Diamondhead to handle.

title: Animo Farm
description: Ben stumbles into Dr. Animo's secret lab now ruled by his superior mutants, the Alphas, and must help the lesser animals escape while stuck as Stinkfly.

title: Clown College
description: While tailgating at a State U. homecoming football game, Ben teams up with Grandpa Max's old college buddies to keep the crazy clown Zombozo from robbing the stadium blind at halftime.

title: Bring Me the Spark of Optimus Prime Part 1
description: The Decepticons compete to be the first to bring Megatron Optimus Prime's spark while Hot Rod chases the "Moon Cheetah."

title: The Gilded Path
description: The headquarters to the resistance is breached and Lloyd scrambles to avoid capture. Meanwhile, the Ninja are caught by Heavy Metal, but find an unlikely ally.

title: Horror Club
description: Steven goes to the lighthouse to watch scary movies with Ronaldo, Lars and Sadie.

title: Hand Zombie
description: After Starfire kisses his hand, Robin vows to never wash it again.

title: Haunted RV
description: After Uncle Grandpa's Haunted House spirals out of control, the gang must save the teenagers stuck inside.

title: The Curse
description: Gumball experiences an impossibly unfortunate chain of events.

title: Block Party
description: Apple and Onion have to outwit a mean duck who's taken over their building's roof.

title: Costume Contest
description: Sick of losing the costume contest to the Hive Five every year, the Titans hatch a scheme to win.

title: Subterranean Homesick Blues/Honey Struck
description: Subterranean Homesick Blues: The AO return home to learn that no time has passed but they soon discover their knowledge of brawling has gotten years more advanced./Honey Struck: After Strata is sent packing the AO discover that they have picked up a hitchhiker a Panda-like Bakugan who is nothing but sticky trouble.

title: Need for Speed
description: Touring Yellowstone, Ben uncovers a plot by the fast & furious LaGrange to find treasure buried below the national park, but with a little help from Old Faithful, Overflow is able to douse LaGrange's dreams.

title: Fathers and Friends/Midsummer Nightmare
description: Midsummer Nightmare: Drago and the other AO Bakugan face an unseen threat with earth shattering power only to be left wondering if it was all a dream./Father's and Fiends: Osamu Kazami comes to take his son Shun back home and finds a defiance he hadn't counted on.

title: Bajo los reflectores
description: Cuando la reportera Verónica Venegas, madre de Lia, hace un reportaje acerca de Los Fantásticos, Strata El Cazador intenta capturar a Hydorous.

title: El eslabon mas debil
description: Lloyd le paga con la misma moneda a Harumi para quitarle el poder a su padre, y los Ninjas aprenden lo que se necesita para ser un Cazador de Dragones.

title: Lab Cat
description: Dr. Fox's robot helpers go on strike, so Unikitty and Puppycorn volunteer to be her lab rats, er, research assistants in a bold new experiment rocketing them into space! But as the mission grows more dangerous, Dr. Fox is forced to choose between the scientific breakthrough of her dreams and ever seeing her friends again!

title: Hostile Take Over/The Big Bounce
description: Hostile Take Over: After more unsuccessful attempts to harness Core Cell energy the AO must battle their own Bakugan with AAAnimus tech in order to save them./The Big Bounce: The AO confront Philomena with concerns about her control over the Core Cell energy and are fired in the most unceremonious of manners.

title: Have I Got a Deal for You
description: Ben and Rook must stop a giant rampaging alien from destroying Bellwood while dealing with a peace-loving alien-rights activist who doesn't want it hurt. (Introducing Hokestar, Solid Plugg 1st appearance, Pax, Sunder.)

title: Pancake's Bus Tour
description: Apple and Onion go on a guided bus tour as part of their plan to get Apple's shoe back.

title: Omni-Tricked
description: Ben's vacation to Portland is cut short when he discovers an 11th alien while battling a Dr. Animo Mega-Creature. But when the fight leaves his Omnitrix on the fritz cycling through all 11 aliens, Max seeks help from an old friend to fix the Omnitrix as other dangerous forces seek it including a mysterious alien that's the same species as the 11th alien, Vilgax!

title: Bienvenido a la Zona Zombozo
description: Durante tiempos medievales, el equipo Tennyson debe esforzarse por recordar que no están en el pasado, sino en una feria renacentista, idonde el "Rey Zombozo" ha hipnotizado a sus invitados para que crean que viven en el pasado!

title: Sea of Tranquility Part 1
description: Optimus Prime and the Autobots battle Megatron and the Deceptions on Earth's Moon.

title: Omni-Truco
description: Ben debe interrumpir sus vacaciones en Portland cuando descubre un 11mo alien al luchar contra la mega criatura del Dr. Animal. Pero, como la lucha deja a su Omnitrix todo estropeado pasando por los 11 aliens, Max pide ayuda a un viejo amigo para que repare el Omnitrix, que es perseguido por otras fuerzas peligrosas, entre ellas un alien misterioso de la misma especie que el 11mo alien...iVilgax!

title: A Made Up Story
description: Someone is defacing all the posters and statues of Townsville with make-up. Can the girls stop this makeover takeover or will they get the blush off?

title: Lightfall Part 2
description: Lord Obsidian attacks the Lighthouse, but Mega Man overcomes his insecurity and works with his family to repel the big bad, who's rescued at the last second by a mysterious lieutenant, Namagem.

title: Hotdog's Movie Premiere
description: Apple and Onion square off against a no-nonsense security guard after they're banned from the premiere of their friend Hot Dog's new movie.

title: Having the Timeout of Our Lives
description: Owen forms a special bond with Duncan after having loads of fun with him during their timeouts.

title: Head Chef
description: Mao Mao faces off with Badgerclops in a competition to determine whether cooking (and being a hero) is an art or a science.

title: #TrianguloDeOdio
description: Cuando la exnovia de Hal aparece en el partido de bienvenida de la preparatoria Metrópolis y se enfurece por amor, convertida en la villana Star Sapphire, Jessica comienza a cuestionar sus propias tácticas no violentas.
originalseriesname: DC Super Hero Girls en Espanol

title: Crece
description: Mientras todo el mundo celebra a Valentino porque le creció su primer vello facial, Vic se pone celoso y recurre a métodos mágicos para dejarse crecer el bigote y competir por la atención.

title: Unboxing Part 1
description: Axel ventures into his uncle's strictly off-limits basement lab in hopes of fixing a broken toy and ends up unleashing living ones instead: the renegade Madcap and a whole team of superpowered toys dedicated to stopping him!

title: Trials Part 1
description: Following the network of GroundBridges left by the Allspark, Optimus and Megatron finally discover the Allspark, and its Guardian, Cheetor.

title: A New Don
description: When Vic & Val discover that Don isn't really himself, it's up to them to use his kooky codex of conspiracies to save him.

title: Una leccion para todos
description: Los Fantásticos le enseñan a unos chicos del vecindario a no imitar a los demás. Por ejemplo, a quienes utilizan a sus Bakugan con fines frívolos.

title: The Ghouls
description: It's Halloween in Elmore. As the kids go trick or treating we see what everyone in town is up to. The ghosts and ghouls are finding it increasingly difficult to scare children, and are only scaring part-time. Can Gumball and Darwin help them get their scare back?

title: Tips
description: Apple and Onion have to find a way to ride the Hot Air Balloon which is in their town for one day only.

title: Fool Moon
description: Strange things start happening when Uncle Grandpa installs a moon roof in the RV.

title: Stratified/Maze Daze
description: Stratified: The AO embark on a mission into the mysterious labyrinth world of Vestroia to find Strata the Hunter and free the Bakugan he has imprisoned./Maze Daze: Lost in the maze of Vestroia the AO encounter powerful forces that seem to be struggling for control over the alien landscape.

title: Bloqueo de Tránsito
description: Cuando un paso elevado colapsa sobre la autopista, el equipo Tennyson queda varado en un embotellamiento junto con Simon Sez y familia. Pero cuando Ben y Simon se alían para enfrentar juntos al atasco, Simon solo consigue que las cosas sean mucho, pero mucho peores.

title: Matter of the Mind/Core Cell
description: Matter of Mind: Drago leads the Bakugan against the threat of Tiko to protect a powerful energy source called the Core Cell./Core Cell: The AO defend the Core Cell from an attack by Tiko and in a last ditch effort to save it Dan manages to evolve Drago into his L2 form.

title: Hole in 10
description: While mini-golfing, Ben is attacked by the Ground Hawgs, a gang of Dr. Animo mutants turned bikers. When the Hawgs realize the faux mini-golf village isn't an actual town, Ben must go alien to stop them before they set their sights on the real city down the road.

title: Welcome to the Underworld 2
description: After Vic loses a wrestling match, V&V journey to the underworld to seek advice from their uncle, a famous wrestler named El Toro.

title: El poder interior
description: Masato Kazami vuelve junto con los guardaespaldas de la familia para llevar a Shun a Japón, pero esta vez, Shun y Hydorous tienen una sorpresa preparada.

title: Xingo
description: Ben está muy interesado en una maratón de Spazz, su dibujo animado favorito, pero cuando se transforma en Upgrade para mejorar la señal de televisión, el protagonista de Spazz salta de su dimensión animada hacia la nuestra...iy trae consigo un caos demente!

title: Monster Visit
description: The monsters get nervous when their Godmonster comes for a visit.

title: Pegatrix
description: Lia no concuerda con las técnicas de Pegatrix, pero durante una intensa batalla, debe aprender a confiar en los conocimientos de su Bakugan.

title: El Relopulpo
description: En una pacífica ciudad costera, Ben no solo debe enfrentarse a Vapor Smythe -su arcaico antagonista- y a su última creación, el Relopulpo... isino que también debe enfrentarse a su temor más profundo y oscuro: los calamares!

title: Luces Brillantes, Corazones Oscuros
description: Ben, Gwen y Max hacen una parada en el cementerio falso en el que se filma el programa de televisión favorito de Gwen, pero cuando Ben descubre que su protagonista, Michael Morningstar, es un vampiro de la energía, se transforma en alienígena para mostrarle al mundo quién es la verdadera estrella del programa: Fuego.

title: Forever Road
description: During a drag race, Ben hopes to stay neck and neck with Vin Ethanol and La Grange as XLR8, but when his watch keeps shorting out, our hero must get creative if he is to keep up with his fast and furious foes!

title: Terror Tales of the Park VI
description: In Regular Show's sixth installment of "Terror Tales," the guys gather in the house on the Dome and tell scary Halloween stories just like ol' times, only this Halloween, the stories have an extra terrifying, science fiction twist.

title: Orangusnake Begins
description: Mao Mao goads Orangusnake and the Sky Pirates into becoming truly terrible villains worthy of a legendary hero such as himself.

title: Necesidad De Velocidad
description: De paseo por Yellowstone, Ben descubre el plan del rápido y furioso LaGrange para encontrar un tesoro enterrado bajo el parque nacional. Pero con una ayudita del géiser Viejo Fiel, Overflow logra empapar los sueños de LaGrange.

title: Conduciendo A La Locura
description: Cuando la Chatarra se rompe en un parque de casas rodantes, Ben descubre que se encuentran en la última etapa del Cali 10 Hundred-una carrera de autos épica todo terreno-en la que LaGrange, el piloto demente, ha regresado en busca de venganza contra aquellos que lo descalificaron hace años.

title: Nightmare Hospital
description: Steven and Connie sneak into a hospital to recover Rose's Sword.

title: Zombozo-Land
description: Ben, Gwen and Max revisit their favorite amusement park, renovated and re-branded as AdrenaWORLD! Unfortunately, the new management is Zombozo and his trio of new henchmen! He's got a plan to hypnotize everyone in the park to form a criminal army. Ben has to set aside his desire to ride every ride in the park and make things right.

title: Costume Crisis
description: Uncle Grandpa makes improvements to a kid's Halloween costume.

title: E. Nigma, Consulting Detective
description: When the Joker traps Batman, the Justice League decides against their better judgment to allow Riddler, who is trying to go straight, to help them track him down.

title: Xingo
description: Ben is more interested in a marathon of his favorite cartoon show, "Xingo", but when Ben goes Upgrade to get a better signal, the titular Xingo leaps from his animated dimension to ours, bringing mad chaos with him!

title: Visita Monstruosa
description: Los monstruos se ponen nerviosos cuando su Dios monstruo llega de visita.

title: The Poltergeist
description: Gumball and Darwin give Mr Robinson a home and end up saving his marriage.

title: Panda's Art
description: Panda paints a portrait of Charlie and it's a hit with his art class. But after an art dealer offers to buy the painting, Panda has to get it back from Charlie.

title: Villain Time
description: Ben must go alien to save the Hoover Dam from disaster, but when tough guy hero Tim Buktu swoops in to "help", Ben must figure out if Tim is friend… or foe.

title: Mushroom Menace
description: The Mysterious Hooded Woman wants the Warriors For Hire to defend her giant pumpkin home from the dreaded Smashroom Mushroom, but Vambre and Prohyas can't complete their mission without help from Zombie Pumpkin Magisword!

title: Stakes Part 5: May I Come In?
description: Finn, Jake, Marceline, and PB set out to hunt down the Vamps. But who is hunting them?

title: Burger Run/Monkey See, Monkey Don't
description: Burger Run: When the local Burger Joint is being threatened by a rogue Bakugan, Dan steps up to save the day and the burgers!/Monkey See, Monkey Don't: The AO stop neighborhood kids from copycat behavior (namely, using their Bakugan for frivolous reasons).

title: The Zone
description: Unikitty keeps losing at video games to her little brother Puppycorn, so she acquires a super-powered video game controller from Dr. Fox to help. To her surprise, it actually controls other people, and the castle goes into lockdown like a real-world video game! At first it seems fun, but will she learn that life isn't a game?

title: Waterfilter
description: Ben, Gwen, and Max's trip to Niagara Falls is cut short by the horrid Hydromanders, creatures menacing them and their fellow tourists.

title: Ben 24hrs
description: When Ben (and Gwen!) attempt to stay up all night for Adrenaland, the only theme park open 24/7, he not only fails to utilize his alien powers to stay awake, but his "sleep-alien-ing" causes disaster after disaster that Gwen must fix before things get way out of hand.

title: La Celula Nucleo
description: Los Fantásticos defienden la Célula Núcleo de un ataque de Tiko, y en el último intento de Dan por salvarla, él y Drago logran liberar un nuevo poder.

title: #FightAtTheMuseum
description: Supergirl always relies on her strength, but she'll need more than brawn to stop brainy Catwoman from stealing valuable gems from the local science museum.

title: Ganas de Explorar
description: La misión de Craig de mapear el Arroyo entero los lleva a él y a sus amigos a arboleda traicionera de Hiedra Venenosa
originalseriesname: Craig of the Creek en Espanol

title: Demonios internos
description: Los Fantásticos encuentran la forma de salir de Vestroia, pero descubren que en realidad están en un mundo paralelo.

title: #SweetJustice Part 4
description: When six ordinary girls meet and discover that they each have extraordinary powers, they decide to join forces to take on one of Metropolis's most sinister villains.

title: Brief Career of Lucky Girl
description: When a wizard cos player gets his hands on a real, magical wand at Comic Con, Ben enlists Gwen to help stop Hex from retrieving it by tricking the wicked warlock into thinking she is a powerful magic-wielder in her own right: the one and only Lucky Girl!

title: The Demon
description: Chloe and Ice Bear accidentally lose Chloe's prized hoodie to the ferocious dog next store. They go on a mission to get it back.

title: 4 on 1
description: Onion's fear of crowds threatens his basketball team's success.

title: Lego DC Super Hero Girls: Brain Drain
description: Missing memories provide an intriguing mystery for everyone's favorite young female heroes in this all-new animated film.  When Supergirl, Wonder Woman, Batgirl, Harley Quinn, Bumblebee, Poison Ivy and Katana suddenly realize they cannot remember a single moment from their Monday at Super Hero High, the young Super Heroes spring into sleuthing action! Suspecting foul-play, they band together to retrace their steps and uncover the mystery of who exactly stole their memories - and, what nefarious plan might be afoot?

title: Steam is the Word
description: In the heart of Silicon Valley, Ben has to stop Victorian villain Steam Smythe from securing an epic power source sealed in a Tesla time capsule.

title: Max Al Maximo
description: Mientras Ben, Gwen y Max van de excursión a una cascada, los Hermanos Bugg regresan con el plan de duplicar a Diamante. Pero cuando su arma láser clonadora le dispara a Max por error-y lo multiplica infinitamente-, Gwen y Ben deben juntar a todos los Maxes y ahuyentar a los Hermanos Bugg a la vez.

title: Bananas y Queso
description: Duncan está decidido a evitar que el dúo Banana y Queso se presente en la guardería.

title: Hot Dog estrena su pelicula
description: Cuando unos guardias de seguridad muy serios los echan del estreno de la nueva película de su amigo Hot Dog, Manzana y Cebollín se preparan para pelear.

title: Dog Daze/In Focus
description: Dog Daze: Lightning discovers a new Bakugan, Artulean, leading to an unhealthy rivalry with Howlkor./In Focus: While Lia's newswoman mom does an expose on the AO Strata the Hunter tries to capture Hydorous.

title: Lightfall Part 1
description: The mysterious Lord Obsidian calls Mega Man a traitor to robots and challenges him to a duel. An overconfident Mega Man is humbled by this mysterious new villain.

title: Todo Mojado
description: Nadie le cree a Ben cuando insiste en que uno de los demás clientes que aguarda en la fila del parque acuático es la malvada Frightwig disfrazada de niña común. Por eso, Ben debe demostrar que dice la verdad mientras protege a los asistentes al parque del plan maestro de la villana: idestruir el parque con su propia presión acuática!

title: CarolQuest
description: Carol is forced to bring KO along as she defends the Plaza from a new threat.

title: Frybo
description: Steven helps a Boardie kid with his grueling job by using a magical gem shard that can bring clothing to life.

title: Adventures in Babysitting
description: Ben, Gwen, and Max meet a family that appears to be a mirror image of them, but when Max goes off on a hike with their matriarch, Maxine, Ben is forced to babysit Simon Sez, a brat with a Billy Billions designed backpack  that turns him into a formidable robot.

title: Que ocurre con Dan
description: Cuando Dan se comporta de forma extraña con los Fantásticos, Lightning olfatea la verdad: iUn impostor!

title: Ghosthaste
description: Vambre becomes enamored of a poltergeist within Ghost Magisword and Prohyas must save her before his sister becomes a ghost herself!

title: Recipe for Disaster
description: During Chefapalooza in the Rocky Mountains, three famous chefs and infamous bad-guys, The Tri-Chefta, hunt down Wildvine in hopes of creating their most exotic dish to date.

title: La sed de poder
description: Tras una discusión entre Wynton y Dan, el coronel Tripp controla la mente de Wynton para que ataque la ciudad con Lupitheon. Esto inicia una guerra entre Los Fantásticos y el ejército.

title: Festival de Cine
description: iEs la noche del estreno en el Festival de Cine de Unireino! Todo el mundo está entusiasmado por ver lo que hicieron los amigos, especialmente Richard, que se considera el máximo experto en cine y no puede esperar a destrozar todas las películas de los demás. Pero después de interpretar el papel del crítico, ¿será la película de Rick una obra maestra o un fracaso?

title: Trick or Threat
description: Four kids in Justice League costumes are trick or treating on Halloween when they investigate a spooky house. As dangers befalls them inside, they come to realize that maybe they're not kids at all, but real Justice Leaguers under a spell.

title: Sale el Don
description: Cuando Vic y Val descubren que Don Jalapeño no es realmente él mismo, depende de ellos usar el alocado libro de conspiraciones de Don para salvarlo.

title: El baul de los recuerdos
description: Al ser confrontada por China Riot, Lia logra evolucionar a Pegatrix cuando comprende la verdadera razón de su obsesión por las cámaras.

title: Dark Birth Part 1
description: While Starscream acquires new power through the Allspark, the Autobots mistakenly assume Starscream is still under Megatron's command.

title: Olvideti
description: Ben, Gwen y Max van de excursión en busca de un Forgeti legendario, un yeti que hace que las personas se olviden de que lo vieron, pero cuando el Doctor Ánimo reúne a los Forgeti para su plan de robar bancos sin que nadie los recuerde, Ben aprende muy pronto que el Forgeti es más que un simple mito.

title: Cortando Camino
description: Ben habla con Geezer Bob para hacer alguna tarea de jardín y así ganar un poco de dinero, pero cuando Ben se transforma en Upgrade para convertir la podadora de césped en una cortadora súper rápida, por accidente despierta la ira de los vecinos gnomos de Bob: los diminutos y aterradoramente obstinados duendes de Billy Bob.

title: Story, Bored
description: During a book signing at a medieval castle, Ben must stop Hex from getting his hands on a grimoire that can fuse its user with mythical beasts, creating monstrous hybrids!

title: The Origins
description: When Mom and Dad struggle to keep hyperactive, toddler-aged Gumball from trashing the house and exhausting them, they decide to buy him a pet. It works, but there's a problem: every goldfish they get him is short-lived, and inevitably ends up being flushed down the toilet.

title: Vengeance Is Mine!
description: Aspheera arrives at the Monastery of Spinjitzu and confronts Wu, forcing one of the ninja to make a heroic sacrifice.

title: Computer Vampire
description: Oscar finds a mysterious old video game in the library.

title: The Weakest Link
description: Lloyd turns the tables on Harumi to take his father's power away, and the Ninja learn what it takes to be a Dragon Hunter.

title: #SweetJustice Part 3
description: When six ordinary girls meet and discover that they each have extraordinary powers, they decide to join forces to take on one of Metropolis's most sinister villains.

title: Perdidas y ganancias
description: Un promotor llamado Everett Ray quiere convencer a Los Fantásticos de ingresar a una liga oficial de Batallas Bakugan.

title: Que No Pare La Musica
description: Ben y Gwen están entusiasmados por ir al concierto de EDM en el Día de la Tierra en Portland, hasta que Lord Decibel, el villano que manipula el sonido, se apodera del concierto cuando intenta usar el sonido como un arma para destruir el planeta.

title: Hora De Ser Villano
description: Ben debe transformarse en alienígena para evitar un desastre en la represa Hoover, pero cuando Tim Buktu, el heroico tipo rudo, se precipita para ayudar, Ben debe descubrir si Tim es su amigo...o su enemigo.

title: Un almuerzo inesperado
description: Cuando el Restaurante de Hamburguesas es amenazado por un violento Bakugan, Dan llega para salvar el día...y las hamburguesas.

title: All Wet
description: No one believes Ben when he insists that one of the other patrons waiting in line at the World of Wet Water Park is the nefarious Frightwig disguised as a common girl. So Ben must prove his case while protecting park goers from her master plan: to destroy the park with its own water pressure!

title: Stratificados
description: Los Fantásticos emprenden una misión en el misterioso mundo laberíntico de Vestroia para buscar a Strata El Cazador y liberar a los Bakugan que tiene presos.

title: The Origins Part 2
description: Via the sewers, Darwin finds himself flushed out to sea. He is terrified but determined to make his way back to the Wattersons. However, a fish can't get very far on land so Darwin will have to do millions of years of evolution in a matter of hours if he's going to get home safe and sound.

title: Malos actores
description: Alguien expone a Dan por mentir acerca de la evolución de Drago, mientras el equipo se enfrenta a Duran Dane y su desdichado Bakugan, Nillious.

title: El Libro Final
description: El último libro de fantasía de la serie favorita de Kelsey desaparece de la biblioteca. Por eso, Craig decide ayudarla a resolver el misterio de quién se lo llevó.
originalseriesname: Craig of the Creek en Espanol

title: The Gift
description: The girls must replace the Professor's Christmas present on Christmas Eve.

title: Apple's in Trouble
description: Apple is challenged to a fight by a grumpy Cheesesteak, so he and Onion go on a quest to find the source of Cheesesteak's grumpiness.

title: El Lider Del Ring
description: Cuando Ben tiene una racha ganadora en un videojuego, se le ocurre una idea para ganar un partido real de lucha, hasta que un luchador intimidante decide convertirlo en un verdadero desafío.

title: El castigo de mi vida
description: Owen forma un nexo especial con Duncan después de que ambos se divirtieran mucho durante sus castigos.

title: Charlie's Halloween Thing 2
description: Charlie tells some scary stories featuring the Bears and their friends.

title: The Filth
description: Ben is tasked with cleaning the Rust Bucket. But when he is tricked into letting the villainous and vile Fly Guys steal it, he must chase them down before they create an unstoppable maggot monster with sights firmly set on destroying Las Vegas.

title: Framing Device/Bad Actors
description: Framing Device: When confronted by China Riot Lia learns to evolve Pegatrix after realizing the true meaning behind her filming obsession./Bad Actors: Dan tries to lie about evolving Drago and gets exposed while the team face off against Duran Dane and his unhappy Bakugan Nillious.

title: Atrapados en la jungla
description: Aún perdidos en Vestroia, Los Fantásticos experimentan los efectos de la Célula Núcleo que altera sus cuerpos, y se encuentran cara a cara con el monstruo Bakugan, Tiko.

title: A Devil on Your Shoulder/Vestral Visions
description: A Devil on Your Shoulder: Near giving up, Magnus gains new strength and insight on the AO's mission to find Core Cells that will eventually lead him down a dark hole./Vestral Visions: Drago's sickness leads Dan to a revelation that there is an ailing Core Cell and if they can't find a cure, the planet itself may falter.

title: Encantadas
description: Durante una comida familiar en un campamento forestal, Charmcaster usa su magia para cambiar de lugar con Gwen, pero cuando Ben descubre a "Charmcaster" husmeando, ataca, sin darse cuenta de que en realidad es su hechizada prima.

title: Firstbourne
description: Emperor Garmadon has taken control of Ninjago City where Lloyd retreats to the shadows. Meanwhile, the other Ninja and Young Wu are shipwrecked in the Realm of Oni & Dragon and find they are not alone.

title: Bright Lights, Black Hearts
description: Ben, Gwen, and Max stop by the graveyard set of Gwen's favorite TV show, The Unalivers, but when Ben discovers its lead, Michael Morningstar, is an energy vampire he goes alien to show the world the real star of the show: Heatblast.

title: Midnight at the Mayor's Mansion
description: When the Mayor's mansion is stalked by a vicious, ghostly monster, he calls the Powerpuff Girls for help.

title: Hogar, dulce hogar
description: Los Fantásticos vuelven a casa y se dan cuenta de que el tiempo no ha pasado. Pronto descubren que su conocimiento acerca de las batallas ha aumentado de forma exponencial.

title: Mask of Power/Story Holes
description:
Mask of Power: Philomena Dusk from AAAnimus Corp. hires Magnus and gives him a control implant to bolster the power of his Bakugan to defeat Dan./Story Holes:  
A cryptic call leads the AO in search of a missing Bakugan but they soon realize the call was actually a test from a mysterious benefactor.

title: #MeetTheCheetah
description: Barbara Minerva is super-jealous of  "little Miss Perfect" Diana Prince. But when she uses an ancient artifact from her dad's collection to place a curse on Diana, it turns out that Diana's not the one who's cursed. It's Barbara.

title: Too Many Unikittys
description: Unikitty comes to the conclusion that everyone would be a lot happier if they would just think the way she does, and with Dr. Fox's help, maybe they can! Unikitty copies her brainwaves into all her friends and turns them Unikitty-fied, so everyone can always be positive! But soon Unikitty quickly realizes there can be too much of a good Princess!

title: Franken-Fight
description: Ben hops into the Rustbuggy for a driving lesson along the sand dunes of Cape Cod, but he takes a freaky switchback turn when the Rustbuggy is mutated into a motor-monster by Bootleg, another alien transformation of Kevin 11, with powers similar to Upgrade!

title: Bad Moon Rising Part 2
description: The Autobots work to stop the Moon from crashing into the Earth as Starscream must reckon with betraying Megatron.

title: Ken 10
description: We're back in the future with Ben 10K, and this time he has a son, Ken. On Ken's tenth birthday, Ben gives him his very own Omnitrix. Ben must come to learn to trust Ken with the power of the Omnitrix. Along the way, Ken befriends a kid named Devlin. Devlin turns out to be Kevin 11's son and was merely using Ken so he could break his dad out of the Null Void. Ben 10K and Ken then team up to take down Kevin 11. As for Devlin, he comes to realize his dad is a jerk, and realizes the error of his ways. He's able to redeem himself, proving he's a good kid and joining forces with "Team Tennyson."

title: El hijo prodigo
description: Mientras los Fantásticos intentan evolucionar a sus Bakugan como lo hizo Dan con Drago, el primo de Shun, Masato, llega a la ciudad para llevarlo de regreso a Japón.

title: Ben 24 Horas
description: Cuando Ben (iy Gwen!) intenta quedarse despierto toda la noche para ir a Adrenaland -el único parque temático abierto las 24 horas, los siete días de la semana- no solo es incapaz de utilizar sus poderes alienígenas para lograr su objetivo, sino que además su estado de adormecimiento alienígena provoca un desastre tras otro, y Gwen debe arreglar las cosas antes de que todo se salga de control.

title: The Beast Inside
description: Ben, Gwen and Max make a return to Max's alma mater but this time it's no homecoming. Dr. Animo has made a scary transformation and found a way to release the very dangerous animal nature of humans, including Max's life-long friend!

title: Bromas pesadas
description: Las constantes bromas pesadas de Wynton colman la paciencia de su Bakugan, Trox, quien decide darle una lección.

title: Riding the Storm Out
description: Ben and Gwen's camping trip is interrupted by the emotionless Weatherheads (Gust-o, Hail-o, & Shock-o) but a malfunctioning Omnitrix firing out a mishmash of aliens may not be the forecast for success.

title: Dawn Before Dusk
description: Dawn Before Dusk, Part 1: The AO meet Benton Dusk discovering that their quiet little corner of the world is about to become much, much larger./Dawn Before Dusk, Part 2: Benton Dusk reveals that the AO have been indentified as persons of interest by powerful corporations including Philomena Dusk's AAAnimus.

title: Enredos perrunos
description: Lightning descubre un nuevo Bakugan, Artulean, y eso desata una fuerte rivalidad entre él y Howlkor.

title: Awesome vs. AAAnimus
description: Awesome V Aaanimus, Part 1: The AO plan on sneaking into AAAnimus and rescuing their Bakugan but are stopped by Benton who offers up an alternate plan./Awesome V Aaanimus, Part 2: The AO team up with Benton Dusk to recapture their stolen Bakugan and free the energy from the Mind Core Cell under the control of AAAnimus.

title: #AdventuresInBunnysitting
description: Zee asks Kara to look after her two magical bunnies, which quickly start to multiply, wreaking havoc all across Metropolis.

title: Trials Part 2
description: Cheetor attempts to judge whether Optimus or Megatron are more worthy of the Allspark, but an unexpected visitor dashes all the bots' plans.

title: El atrapador
description: Dan y Wynton se encuentran con la posible ubicación secreta de la Célula Núcleo, y con el coronel Tripp, que busca apoderarse de la fuente de energía.

title: #ShockItToMe
description: Leslie Willis, the meanest girl in school, becomes a social media sensation by posting mean-spirited videos on her MetropoVids channel, causing Wonder Woman to question the moral integrity of the people who live in the World of Man.

title: Ninos vergonzosos
description: Owen teme perder a su mejor amigo Noah que se va a una escuela militar.

title: Hip hip Hurra
description: Bridgette tiene hipo y está desesperada por librarse de ellos.

title: Sr. Luna
description: Wynton encuentra un nuevo Bakugan que resulta difícil de controlar, y las cosas se complican cuando el Coronel Tripp se apodera de Trox.

title: High Flying Hostiles/Backfire Brawl
description: High Flying Hostiles: While escorting the Mind Core Cell to AAAnimus Campus, the AO are attacked by Masato Kazami and his Body Guards./Backfire Brawl: Philomena's attempt to refocus the Mind Core Cell's power backfires and the AO must fight their fellow employees inside the AAAnimus Campus.

title: Drive You Crazy
description: After the Rust Bucket breaks down at a Mobile Home Park, Ben discovers they've stumbled on to the last leg of the Cali 10 Hundred, an epic, off-road auto race where mad driver Le Grange has returned for revenge against those that disqualified him years ago.

title: Muerto De Miedo
description: Cuando la Chatarra se queda sin gasolina en una carretera brumosa de la Costa Este, Ben, Gwen y Max se ven obligados a pasar la noche en un hotel amenazado por Creepy Carl, iun experto en folclore de la zona que podría ser un fantasma verdadero!

title: DC Super Hero Girls: Super Hero High
description: Supergirl arrives at Super Hero High and struggles to learn to control her new powers. Meanwhile, the Junior Detective Club investigates a mysterious rash of security breaches centered around the teleportation Boom Tubes.

title: The Visitor Part 1
description: Bumblebee searches for any information his fellow Autobots might have regarding a strange creature he saw on the Moon.

title: Starscream's Children Part 2
description: Starscream reveals his scraplet army, incapacitating the Autobots and Decepticons and setting up a show down between him and Cheetor.

title: Jessica Goes to the Creek
description: When Craig and Jessica are locked out of the house, Craig has no choice but to bring his little sister to the Creek.

title: Little Sword of Horrors
description: Prohyas grows a new Magisword from a tiny seed, but doesn't know that his Carnivorous Plant Magisword is a menace to Lyvsherian society until its too late!

title: Captured Clops
description: Badgerclops is tired of his responsibilities at Sheriff's HQ, so he joins the Sky Pirates.

title: Monster Party
description: Enid is faced with a choice when her old friends from Ghoul School show up.

title: Web Weirdos
description: When Finn gets trapped in a giant spider web, he ends up playing marriage counselor to a couple of grumpy arachnids.

title: Bienvenidos al Inframundo Parte 1
description: Después de que Vic pierde una pelea de lucha libre, V&V viajan al inframundo para buscar el consejo de su tío, un famoso luchador llamado El Toro.

title: Charlie's Halloween Thing
description: Charlie hosts an evening of spooky stories starring the Bears.

title: No sin mis choco-lletas
description: Noah intenta rescatar los chocolates que Owen olvidó afuera.

title: Inglorious Toddlers
description: Owen fears he's about to lose his BFF Noah to a gifted military school.

title: Radio Ninjago libre
description: Lloyd deberá encontrar su voz mientras lidera una pequeña resistencia para capturar las señales de transmisión en Ciudad Ninjago. Mientras tanto en el Primer Reino, el Barón de Hierro lleva a los Ninjas en una cacería de dragones.

title: You're It
description: A vicious game of tag wreaks havoc on the Creek, claiming Kelsey as the next it.

title: Padres y amigos
description: Osamu Kazami viene para llevarse a su hijo Shun a casa y se encuentra con un obstáculo que no había contemplado.

title: Sea of Tranquility Part 2
description: The Autobots struggle to stop the Decepticon's planet-cracking weapon as it targets Earth.

title: #SuperWho?
description: Overwhelmed by the amount of Superman coverage in Metropolis, Supergirl decides to get out there and really show the city what she can do. But when Superman inadvertently puts everyone in harm's way, Supergirl has to decide whether to do what's good for the people or what's good for her ego.

title: Something I Ate
description: Ben, Gwen, and Max go on a tour of the impervious Fort Knox, but when Dr. Animo sicks a hungry ani-mutate on the Fort, Ben must stop it before it gobbles up the nation's monitory standard!

title: Cat Fingers
description: Steven attempts to master the power of shape shifting, but can only shape shift his fingers into tiny cat heads.

title: Los Cadejos
description: Val le guarda rencor a Vic, lo cual atrae sin querer a un malvado cadejo, una bestia mitológica parecida a un lobo.

title: La Traes
description: Un despiadado juego de persecución desata un caos en el Arroyo, y se declara a Kelsey como la próxima perseguidora.
originalseriesname: Craig of the Creek en Espanol

title: Bananas & Cheese
description: Duncan is determined to stop the musical duo Bananas & Cheese from coming to the daycare.

title: The So-Bad-Ical
description: When a new substitute shows up, KO and Dendy decide they need to get their old teacher back.

title: Aventuras Cuidando Ninos
description: Ben, Gwen y Max se encuentran con una familia que parece ser un reflejo de ellos. Pero cuando Max sale a caminar con su matriarca, Maxine, Ben se ve obligado a cuidar a Simon Sez, un malcriado con una mochila diseñada por Billy Billones, que lo convierte en un robot formidable.

title: Cirque-Us
description: After saving a State University Alumni ribbon cutting ceremony, Ben becomes the guest of honor at the upcoming Gala, but when the cirque entertainment turns out be Zombozo, in disguise, Ben must not only defeat the evil clown but his mysterious new sidekick, Pirouette!

title: Phased and Confused
description: When members of the Justice League are affected by the Phantom Zone ray and become phantom-like, their only hope for freedom is to somehow get a message to Booster Gold.

title: Parley Part 2
description: The Autobot-Decepticon peace talks breaks down after Slipstream returns with a dire warning.

title: Spooky Boo
description: After Clarence leads a few neighborhood kids through his homemade haunted house, Chelsea suggests they go to the high school kids haunted house for some real scares. When the gang makes a wrong turn they find themselves in a mysterious house on a hill full of creepy sounds, ghoulish shadows and mutant rat men!

title: A Real Steal/Lightning Unleashed
description: A Real Steal: Dan embarks on a solo adventure to outdo Magnus's new team of Bakugan Brawlers and winds up having to be saved by them instead./Lightning Unleashed: Lightning uncovers the Mind Core Cell buried beneath the Earth and battles Stata the Hunter in an effort to protect its secret.

title: Aventura en el laberinto
description: Perdidos en el laberinto de Vestroia, Los Fantásticos se enfrentan a poderosas fuerzas que parecen luchar por el control del planeta.

title: Custody Battle/City of Nutsville
description: Custody Battle: Mojo discovers the Rowdyruff Boys are back and is determined to show them that he is a more evil dad than Him./The City of Nutsville: The squirrels of Townsville are chirping mad! But when Bubbles loses her ability to speak a squirrel, the girls don't know how to calm the rodents down.

title: Tummy Trouble
description: When the Incursean armada kidnaps the Gourmand Queen, Ben and Rook must get the warring Gormand factions to work together to save her and stop the Incursean invasion.

title: All Jungled Up/Outer Demons
description: All Jungled Up: Still lost in Vestroia the AO experience mind altering effects of the nearby Core Cell and come face to face with the Bakuzon monster Tiko./Outer Demons: The AO find the doorway out of Vestroia only to learn they have entered a mirror world of their own imagining created by the Core Cell.

title: Frenemies/Strata's Fear
description: Frenemies: Two new Bakugan Brawlers, Shun and Magnus, try out for the AO./Strata's Fear: The AO solve the mystery of a kid's missing Bakugan and meet a Bakugan Hunter named Strata.

title: Manzana esta en Problemas
description: Bistec con Queso, malhumorado, desafía a Manzana a una pelea. De ese modo, Manzana puede embarcarse con Cebollín en una misión para encontrar el origen del malhumor de Bistec con Queso.

title: A New Life
description: Apple and Onion both leave their homes and follow their dreams to the big city but things don't go quite to plan.

title: Hic Hic Hooray
description: Bridgette gets the hiccups and becomes desperate to get rid of them.

title: Demasiados Tesoros
description: Con la esperanza de reparar su fuerte, Craig consigue la ayuda de Los Veloces Diez para llevarlos hasta la legendaria pila de basura.
originalseriesname: Craig of the Creek en Espanol

title: Regular Show: Terror Tales of the Park
description: The park can be a very scary place at night.

title: Vapor Es La Palabra
description: En el corazón de Silicon Valley, Ben debe impedir que Vapor Smythe, el villano victoriano, consiga una fuente de poder épica sellada en una cápsula del tiempo diseñada por Tesla.

title: The Throw Down/Brawl for It All
description: The Throw Down: Lightning reveals his discovery of the Mind Core Cell but the AO arrive only to discover that Magnus has already beaten them to it./Brawl for It All: With both team's Bakugan knocked into a hibernation state by the Mind Core Cell only Dan and Magnus remain locked in a brawl for it all!

title: Escape from Beyond the Cosmic
description: When Clarence accidentally breaks a local arcade game Jeff has become obsessed with, Clarence puts together his own real-life version of the game at home, encouraging Jeff to act out his fantasy in levels created exclusively by Clarence.

title: Lecciones para un maestro
description: Cuando el Barón de Hierro obliga a Wu a tomar la Armadura de Dragón, las cosas no salen como se planearon. En Ninjago, hay un límite de lo que Lloyd puede soportar mientras se aferra a la esperanza del regreso de los Ninjas.

title: #LaDulceJusticia - Primera parte
description: En el episodio estreno de cuatro partes de la serie, seis chicas comunes y corrientes se conocen y descubren que tienen poderes extraordinarios. Deciden unir sus fuerzas para derrotar a algunos de los villanos más siniestros de Metrópolis.
originalseriesname: DC Super Hero Girls en Espanol

title: The Exit/The Lost and the Cost
description: The Exit: The AO compete with a rival Brawling team for ViewTube hits leading to a "winner take all" brawl./The Lost and the Cost: Everett Ray, a promotor, tries to get the AO to join an official league for Bakugan Battling.

title: El miedo de Strata
description: Los Fantásticos resuelven la misteriosa desaparición del Bakugan de un niño, y conocen a un cazador de Bakugan llamado Strata.

title: Bring Me the Spark of Optimus Prime Part 2
description: Slipstream searches for her missing Seekers while Hot Rod's "Moon Cheetah" chase brings him unexpectedly aboard the Nemesis.

title: A Nightmare on Aberdale Street: Balance's Revenge
description: In this Halloween adventure, Clarence uses a special jack-o-lantern to enter the world of people's dreams. He discovers that something mysterious is causing his friends to have nightmares, and Clarence needs to stop it!

title: The Perfect Team
description: Onion worries his relationship with Apple is in jeopardy when a stray cat enters the picture.

title: Under Siege
description: Having learned Master Wu is the "Treacherous One," the ninja find themselves under siege at the Monastery, trying to protect Wu from the wrath of Aspheera.

title: Industrias Dusk, Parte 1
description: Los Fantásticos conocen a Benton Dusk y descubren que su pequeño mundo está a punto de volverse mucho más grande.

title: Stakes Part 1: Marceline the Vampire Queen
description: Finn & Jake hunt for a shadowy predator and Marceline asks Princess Bubblegum for a huge favor.

title: Tripped Up/Power Tripp
description: Tripped Up: Dan and Wynton stumble on both a possible hidden location of the Mind Core Cell and Colonel Tripp who wants the energy source for himself./Power Tripp: After a falling out with Dan, Wynton is mind-controlled by Tripp who stages an attack to ignite a war between Brawlers and the Military.

title: Una verdad a medias
description: Un críptico correo electrónico lleva a Los Fantásticos en busca de un Bakugan desaparecido, pero pronto se dan cuenta de que el correo era una prueba de un misterioso benefactor.

title: The Visitor Part 2
description: Dino-Mode Grimlock careens out-of-control around the Ark after drinking Wheeljack's hyper-fuel.

title: #SweetJustice Part 2
description: When six ordinary girls meet and discover that they each have extraordinary powers, they decide to join forces to take on one of Metropolis's most sinister villains.

title: La Zona
description: A Unikitty le cuesta mantener la calma cuando juega a videojuegos y entra en La Zona, a diferencia de Puppycorn, su hermano menor. Pero un repentino accidente de laboratorio destroza su consola y ahora, para su sorpresa, el castillo se bloquea como un videojuego del mundo real, icon sus amigos como jugadores! ¿Podrá Unikitty salvar a sus amigos y dominar La Zona antes de que termine el juego?

title: Una extrana conexion
description: Drago lidera a los Bakugan contra la amenaza de Tiko, para proteger una poderosa fuente de energía.

title: Shun Shine/Ronin Son
description: Shun Shine: The AO want to evolve their Bakugan like Dan did with Drago but only Shun finds a way by tapping into the energy of the Mind Core Cell./Ronin Son: When Shun's cousin Masato Kazami claims Hydorous as his intellectual property the AO must battle to keep their friend by their side.

title: Don't Laze Me, Bro
description: Ben and his arch-enemy Billy Billions clash in a duel for supremacy at the world's largest Laser Tag Park, LASER TOWN. But, when Billy inadvertently ignites a robot rebellion, and the lasers are set from tag to disintegrate, their childish game escalates into a full blown war! The two foes find that they must set aside their petty differences and team up in order to make it out alive, let alone save the day!

title: Watchtower Tours
description: When Booster Gold starts to secretly give tours of the Watchtower to make some extra cash, he inadvertently brings in a super villain disguised as a tourist.

title: El bravucon
description: Los Fantásticos deben lidiar con un bravucón que usa a su Bakugan para intimidar a los chicos del vecindario.

title: Merry Moochmas
description: It's wintertime in Aberdale and Clarence is convinced his winter wish for snow in Arizona will come true! However, his classmate Belson along with his grumpy cousin Gary Mooch are a little tougher to convince.

title: Cabeza de Playa
description: Después de viajar a Tampa Beach, Florida, el equipo Tennyson espera poder descansar y relajarse, pero las tempestades sin temperamento, los Climáticos, tienen otros planes que Ben debe frustrar: iconstruir una nueva base en la playa!

title: Attack of Thermometron 9000
description: Axel must wrangle Galileo and Bobbie to shut down a rogue thermostat - improperly upgraded by Slobot - as it plunges the house into extreme hot and cold zones.

title: Mascara de poder
description: Philomena Dusk, de la Corporación AAAnimus, contrata a Magnus y le implanta un dispositivo que aumenta el poder de su Bakugan para derrotar a Dan.

title: 4 a 1
description: El temor de Cebollín a las multitudes amenaza el éxito de su equipo de baloncesto.

title: Max to the Max
description: While Ben, Gwen, and Max hike to a waterfall, the Bugg Brothers are back with a plan to duplicate Diamondhead; but when their cloning ray gun fires on Max instead, multiplying him endlessly, Gwen and Ben must round up all the Maxes while also fighting off the Bugg Brothers.

title: Never Trust a Human
description: A flashback episode tells the story of Young Wu and Young Garmadon meeting Aspheera and teaching her the secrets of Spinjitzu.

title: Welcome to the Underworld 1
description: After Vic loses a wrestling match, V&V journey to the underworld to seek advice from their uncle, a famous wrestler named El Toro.

title: Lectura, Que Aburrido
description: Durante una firma de libros en un castillo medieval, Ben debe impedir que Hex se apodere de un grimorio que puede fusionar a su lector con bestias míticas...iy así crear híbridos monstruosos!

title: Penny Ruda
description: Ben visita el Gran Desfile Anual Big Bacon, pero Penny Heaven, su "amiga" de la infancia, se reúne con la familia para estropear la diversión de Ben con su obsesión por la seguridad. Mientras Ben esquiva las medidas de seguridad extremas de Penny, devela un plan de los HERMANOS BUGG, ique intentan robar helio de los globos del desfile para usarlos en robos de bancos! La insistencia de Penny convierte el ataque en un secuestro accidental, de modo que Ben no solo debe impedir el robo sino también salvar a su "supervisora de seguridad" menos querida.

title: El origen de las especies, Parte 1
description: Dan conoce a su pareja Bakugan, Drago, por primera vez y nos enteramos del "incidente" que ocurrió en la Tierra hace doce años.

title: Bad Moon Rising Part 1
description: Starscream makes a play for leadership of the Deceptions as the Autobots storm the Decepticon's Moon Base.

title: Octi Evil/Geshundfight
description: Octi Evil: The heinous Him toys with Bubbles' mind by speaking to her through Octi, her favorite stuffed animal. Following Him's orders, Bubbles picks a fight with her sisters that lands them all in a time-out./Geshundfight: The Amoeba Boys' ill-conceived plan to stand in Townsville Park all night in the rain leaves them with a nasty virus that's really something to sneeze at.

title: Unboxing Part 2
description: Axel discovers that he can transform into a toy and teams up with his new team of toys to stop Madcap from stealing a Minergy battery.

title: Filtro Acuatico
description: El viaje de Ben, Gwen y Max a las Cataratas del Niágara se ve interrumpido por los horribles Hydromanders: unas criaturas que los amenazan a ellos y a los demás turistas.

title: Fogata Encantada
description: Los campistas deben enfrentar fantasmas creados por ellos mismos, luego de que sus historias de terror cobran vida misteriosamente.

title: Industrias Dusk, Parte 2
description: Benton Dusk revela que Los Fantásticos son considerados personas de interés por poderosas corporaciones como AAAnimus.

title: How to Build a Dragon
description: While Lloyd and the rebels celebrate their successful strike against Emperor Garmadon, in the Realm of Oni and Dragon, the Ninja dare an elaborate escape from the clutches of Iron Baron and his Dragon Hunters.

title: Be a Team
description: Mr. Gar brings in some team building experts to help KO, Enid and Rad.

title: Atrapa la Botella
description: Manzana y Cebollín inventan un nuevo juego que atrae una atención inesperada.

title: Rad Monster Party
description: Ben and Rook enlist the help of intergalactic smuggler Rad Dudesman to fly them through the Anur System—the home of the monstrous aliens!

title: Enter the Wood Man
description: Mega Man accidentally awakens Wood Man, who thinks it's still the Hard Age, sets off on a path of destruction toward Silicon City.

title: Tomorrow Today
description: When Max drags the kids to see a defunct "House of the Future" built by his childhood idol, Ben discovers Steam Smythe is busy excavating the joint on the search for a powerful device that will allow him to create devastating weapons for his war on progress. Only Max's devotion to his childhood idol and Ben's faith in dreams can save tomorrow... today!

title: Fiesta en la Cuadra
description: Manzana y Cebollín deben ser más astutos que un pato malvado que se apoderó del techo de su edificio.

title: #HateTriangle
description: When Hal's ex-girlfriend shows up at the Metropolis High homecoming game and goes love-ballistic as the villain Star Sapphire, Jessica begins to second-guess her own nonviolent tactics.

title: Terror Tales of the Park IV
description: The park guys try to keep Muscle Man awake with scary stories on a long drive so that they can meet his mom.

title: #LaDulceJusticia - Tercera parte
description: Cuando seis chicas comunes y corrientes descubren que cada una tiene un poder extraordinario diferente, deciden unir fuerzas para derrotar a algunos de los villanos más siniestros de Metrópolis en la parte 3 del episodio estreno.
originalseriesname: DC Super Hero Girls en Espanol

title: La Bestia Interior
description: Ben, Gwen y Max regresan a la universidad de Max, pero esta vez no les dan una cálida bienvenida. El Doctor Ánimo ha hecho una transformación escalofriante y ha descubierto un modo de liberar la peligrosa naturaleza animal de los seres humanos...iincluida la del amigo de toda la vida de Max!

title: Bewitched, Bothered and Bothered Some More!
description: Flonk hires the Warriors to make Witch Way change his brother Helmut from a frog back to human.

title: Billy Billones
description: En Aspen, Colorado, Ben, Gwen y el abuelo Max van de excursión para encontrar al Olvideti. Pero cuando se encuentran con la pista artificial de esquí de Billy Billones, Ben debe luchar contra Billy con la ayuda del propio Olvideti.

title: Forgeti
description: When Gwen drags Ben along on a hike in search of the legendary Forgeti, a yeti that makes people forget they ever saw it, Ben is dubious. But with Dr. Animo on the trail of the mythical beast as well, what looks like a hoax becomes a hero time adventure for the ages, if Ben can remember it ever happened.

title: Too Many Treasures
description: Hoping to fix their fort, Craig enlists the 10 Speeds to give them a ride to the legendary Junk Pile.

title: The Squashening
description: To escape a monster, the girls have to tell him a scary story.

title: New Kid
description: Uncle Grandpa gives a kid a haircut that is too cool for school.

title: Un golpe de ternura
description: Después de derrotar a Strata, Los Fantásticos se dan cuenta de que no volvieron solos, sino con un Bakugan parecido a un panda que les dará muchos problemas.

title: Demasiados Unikitties
description: Unikitty llega a la conclusión de que todo el mundo sería mucho más feliz si pensara como ella, iy tal vez pueda lograrlo con la ayuda de la Dra. Fox! Unikitty copia sus ondas cerebrales en todos sus amigos y los Unikittyfica, para que todos puedan ser siempre positivos. Pero pronto, Unikitty se da cuenta de que puede haber un exceso de "buena princesa".

title: Two Lies, One Truth
description: As Lloyd unmasks Mystake for who she truly is, Emperor Garmadon embraces Harumi as his daughter of darkness. Meanwhile, Wu holds onto faith as he leads his friends into dangerous Oni territory in the hope of finding Firstbourne's nest

title: El Equipo Perfecto
description: A Cebollín le preocupa que su relación con Manzana corra peligro cuando un gato callejero entra en su vida.

title: Flirty Phantom
description: Lost in Transylberia, the Warriors come to a haunted house for help and meet a young ghost lady inside that wants to spend the rest of her afterlife with Prohyas!

title: Local Heroes/Pegatrix
description: Local Heroes: After the AO cause accidental destruction Dan's parents question whether the kids should be allowed to keep their Bakugan./Pegatrix: Lia disagrees with her new Bakugan Pegatrix on battle techniques but during a fierce fight Lia must rely on Pegatrix's battle savy.

title: Bad Penny
description: Ben is at the annual Big Bacon Pig Parade, but childhood friend Penny Heaven has met the family to ruin Ben's fun with her safety-obsessed self. While dodging Penny's overzealous safety precautions, Ben uncovers a plot by the Bug Brothers to steal helium from the parade balloons to rob banks with! Penny's badgering turns the heist into an accidental kidnapping so Ben must not only stop the robbery but save his least favorite safety monitor in the process.

title: Regular Show Presents: Terror Tales of the Park II
description: The park can be a very scary place at night.

title: Algo Que Comi
description: Ben, Gwen y Max van de paseo al impenetrable Fort Knox, pero cuando el Doctor Ánimo hace que un animal-mutante hambriento se enferme, iBen debe detenerlo antes de que se devore la reserva monetaria de la nación!

title: Witch's Crew
description: On Halloween Night, Morbucks summons a monster that she didn't expect.

title: The Rooters of All Evil
description: Meet the Rooters, the Black Ops wing of the Plumbers from the Null Void. They've come looking for someone close to Ben, and they mean business!

title: Not Without My Fudgy Lumps
description: Noah tries to rescue the chocolates Owen forgot outside.

title: The Ring Leader
description: While winning big on a Sumo Slammers video game, Ben gets the idea to win a wrestling match for real until an intimidating wrestler named Iron Kyle decides to make it a true challenge.

title: Clarence and Sumo's Rexcellent Adventure
description: On a school trip to the Aberdale Natural History Museum, Clarence and Sumo check out the displays, goof around with the exhibits and even remove a tooth from the T-Rex display.

title: Poppy Rangers
description: Ranger Tabes leads a troop of young girls into a cave expedition, and brings Grizz as their cave expert.

title: Regular Show Presents: Terror Tales of the Park III
description: Each of the park guys want to win a bet by telling the scariest story at a Halloween party.

title: Propinas
description: Luego de destruir por accidente el boleto de Falafel para un concierto, Manzana y Cebollín deben descubrir un modo de evitar la furia de Falafel.

title: Shhh
description: Mientras Ben se relaja en un monasterio con una política de silencio, no puede quedarse callado y, por accidente, despierta a un peligroso Dragón oculto en una recámara secreta bajo los salones sagrados...una tarea que podría ser demasiado para manejar, iincluso para Diamante!

title: Hierro y piedra
description: Cole y Wu Joven intentan liberar a sus amigos, que han sido capturados por una tribu de Cazadores de Dragones. Mientras tanto en Ninjago, Lloyd se reúne con unos viejos amigos que quizás sean aliados valiosos contra el Emperador Garmadon.

title: A Cold Goodbye
description: Having learned Zane is not dead, Master Wu prepares to go after him, but Lloyd and the other ninja take matters into their own hands and defy their Master.

title: Salvando a Faith
description: Lloyd y su equipo planean tomar el control del Oni Titan. Mientras tanto en el Primer Reino, los Ninja caen en las garras del Barón de Hierro y un viejo maestro regresa.

title: Escuela De Payasos
description: Mientras Ben disfruta en el estacionamiento a la salida de un partido de fútbol americano de ex estudiantes de la Universidad de State, se alía con los antiguos compañeros del Abuelo Max para impedir que Zombozo, un payaso demente, le robe a todo el público durante el entretiempo.

title: Home on the Run/Top Slot
description: Home on the Run: We are introduced to Shun's mysterious backstory, his relationship with his industrialist father and desire for a closer knit family./Top Slot: Dan and Shun butt heads on how best to make the AO a real team amidst growing threats including the mysterious Shargo Ronin.

title: Green Destiny
description: The Ninja finally return home and unite to stop Emperor Garmadon, forcing Lloyd to make a decision that will forever change Ninjago.

title: Which Watch
description: After a battle with Kevin gets mysteriously cut short, Ben turns his attention to one upping Gwen at Space Camp. But, when his arch-nemesis, Kevin, returns with his sights strangely set on his cousin, our hero must uncover who is really behind it all, Charmcaster!

title: Bottle Catch
description: Apple and Onion's favorite game attracts some unexpected attention.

title: Gato de laboratorio
description: La Dra. Fox necesita Unikitty y Puppycorn como voluntarios para ser sus ratas de laboratorio, idigo, asistentes de investigación en un nuevo y audaz experimento que los lanzará al espacio! Pero a medida que la misión se vuelve más peligrosa, la Dra. Fox se ve obligada a elegir entre el avance científico de sus sueños y volver a ver a sus amigos.

title: Take 10
description: While trying to film his own indie film, Ben accidentally allows the Bug Gang to go free and when he takes the fight to their hidden lair Ben has to take on their narcissistic leader, the Ant Queen.

title: Let's Watch the Boxmore Show
description: Our heroes discover that the Boxmore security camera feed is the most entertaining thing ever.

title: El origen de las especies, Parte 2
description: Dan y sus amigos ganan la Batalla Bakugan, demostrando que los Fantásticos son nuestros héroes y los mejores Peleadores Bakugan.

title: Vampiro de Computadora
description: Oscar encuentra un videojuego viejo y misterioso en la biblioteca.

title: Rustbucket RIP
description: During a tour of historic Oldeville Ben finds a rare Sumo Slammers card, but when Billy Billions comes to claim the same card Ben has to battle Billy's high-tech drones which have hijacked the Rust Bucket!

title: #Beeline
description: When she stumbles across a villainous plot to blow up a bridge, Bumblebee shies from the challenge of taking on the baddies and reaches out to her friends. But when the other heroes are all indisposed, it'll take every ounce of courage Bumblebee has to rise to the occasion … despite being the smallest of the bunch.

title: Chille Tid
description: Steven and the Crystal Gems try to relax with a slumber party.

title: Just Another Manic Mojo/Mime for a Change
description: Just Another Manic Mojo: The Powerpuff Girls lose their baseball in Mojo's house, offering him the perfect opportunity to destroy these pesky superheroines if he can only get them to sit still./Mime for a Change: An accidental bleach spill turns Rainbow the Clown into the malevolent Mr. Mime. He proceeds to turn Townsville black and white and dead all over.

title: El camino dorado
description: El cuartel general de la resistencia es irrumpido y Lloyd lucha por no ser capturado. Mientras tanto, los Ninjas son capturados por Heavy-Metal, pero encuentran un aliado improbable.

title: Rebelion En La Granja
description: Ben encuentra el laboratorio secreto del Doctor Ánimo -ahora gobernado por los alfas, sus mutantes superiores- y debe ayudar a los animales inferiores mientras está atrapado en forma de Insectoide.

title: Ene-amigos
description: Dos nuevos Peleadores Bakugan, Shun y Magnus, buscan ser parte de Los Fantásticos.

title: Lessons for a Master
description: When Iron Baron forces Wu to retrieve the Dragon Armor, things don't go as planned. In Ninjago, Lloyd can only endure so much as he holds onto hope for the Ninjas' return.

title: Sugar Berry Fever
description: Mao Mao tries to hide his love of cobbler.

title: Stakes Part 6: Take Her Back
description: While Princess Bubblegum searches for a cure for Marceline, Finn & Jake take on one of the Vamps themselves.

title: The Clocktopus
description: In a peaceful coastal town, Ben must not only face the archaic antagonist Steam Smythe and his latest creation, the Clocktopus, but also his deepest, darkest fear: Squids!

title: Washington B.C.
description: Ben must use the Omnitrix to transform into alien heroes to battle Dr. Amino and his transmorphed dinosaurs running rampant in Washington DC.

title: Lego DC Super Hero Girls: Galactic Wonder
description: Wonder Woman has won student of the month at Super Hero High again!  As a special surprise Principal Waller has flown in Wonder Woman's mother, Queen Hippolyta, for a visit. Queen Hippolyta is not happy with what she finds and demands that Wonder Woman return to school at the island paradise of Themyscira. Hoping to take her mind off of her troubles with her mother Wonder Woman, Batgirl and Supergirl decide to investigate a strange electromagnetic anomaly. Their investigation leads them to the hideout of Lena Luthor where they discover a plot between her and Eclipso to transform the planet Earth into a new version of Gemworld!  The girls will have to split up to find the generators scattered around the planet and destroy them. They'll also have to overcome Lena's new breed of mood altering Kryptomites to save the day and convince Queen Hippolyta that Super Hero High is the best school for Wonder Woman!

title: Los Cadejos
description: Val holds a grudge against Vic, unwittingly attracting an evil cadejo, a mythological wolf-like beast.

title: Tutores Bakugan
description: Dan y Wynton conocen a un extraño chico que los lleva a un laberinto subterráneo, donde descubren que el Bakugan del chico ha sido esclavizado.

title: Trading Day
description: When they think each others' lives are easier, the heroes switch roles.

title: Freaky Gwen Ben
description: When Ben interferes with malicious magician Hex's quest for the earth-moving Titan Gloves at a swap meet, he inadvertently switches bodies with Gwen forcing him to walk a mile in her shoes… and vice-versa!

title: Power Cycle
description: After replicating Elec Man's powers, an underslept/overcharged Mega Man goes on a 24/7 hero spree that ends up turning him into his own worst enemy.

title: Como construir un dragon
description: Mientras Lloyd y los rebeldes celebran su exitoso golpe contra el Emperador Garmadon, en el Reino de Oni y Dragón, los Ninjas se aventuran con un elaborado escape de las garras del Barón de Hierro y sus Cazadores de Dragones.

title: El equipo Exit
description: Los Fantásticos compiten por el número de visitas en sus videos con un equipo rival llamado "El equipo Exit" en una batalla donde se juegan el todo por el todo.

title: Zombozolandia
description: Ben, Gwen y Max vuelven a su parque de diversiones favorito... irenovado y rebautizado como AdrenaWORLD! Por desgracia, iel nuevo gerente es Zombozo, y su trío de secuaces! Zombozo planea hipnotizar a todos los visitantes del parque para formar un ejército criminal. Ben tiene que dejar de lado su deseo de subir a todos los juegos del parque y arreglar las cosas.

title: Manana Es Hoy
description: Cuando Max arrastra a los niños a ver una "Casa del futuro" obsoleta construida por su ídolo de la infancia, Ben descubre que Vapor Smythe está ocupado excavando el lugar en busca de un dispositivo poderoso que le permitirá crear armas devastadoras para su guerra en progreso. Solo la devoción de Max por su ídolo de la infancia y la fe de Ben en los sueños puede salvar el mañana...ihoy mismo!

title: Career Opportunities/Punch the Clock
description: Career Opportunities: After defeating Magnus the AO get an offer of employment from a surprising source Philomena Dusk!/Punch the Clock: During a commercial to celebrate their joining the AAAnimus team Dan and the AO rebel before they sellout.

title: Descanse En Paz Rustbucket
description: Durante un tour por la histórica ciudad de Oldeville, Ben encuentra una carta de Sumo Slammers poco común. Pero cuando Billy Billones reclama esa carta, Ben debe luchar contra los drones tecnológicos de Billy, ique secuestraron la Chatarra!

title: Cambio De Edad
description: Durante una parada en la megatienda Shoppë, Nanny Nightmare -una niñera que se volvió loca- transforma a Ben y Gwen en bebés. Y nada la detendrá en su intento de reorganizar el mundo a imagen y semejanza de su guardería.

title: Ghost the Boy
description: Oscar and Hedgehog befriend a ghost who can't remember who he is.

title: Origin of Species
description: Origin of Species, Part 1: Dan meets his partner Bakugan Drago for the first time and we learn about the incident that happened on Earth twelve years ago./Origin of Species, Part 2: Dan and friends win the Bakugan Battle, firmly establishing the Awesome Ones as our heroes and Bakugan Brawlers.

title: Buggin' the Buggs
description: Team Tennyson travel to the Chrysalen Institute for some hot yoga and good vibes, only to find that the Bugg Brothers are on vacation, too, but are the sneaky insectoids really on holiday, or just cooking up yet another silly, yet high stakes scheme?

title: Fiesta de cumpleanos
description: Master Frown, el habitante más pesimista del reino, se roba el deseo de cumpleaños de Puppycorn. Para recuperarlo, Unikitty y Puppycorn tendrán que aventurarse en la tierra más deprimente de la historia: iFrown Town! ¿Conseguirán recuperar el deseo de cumpleaños de manos de Frown antes de que su deseo (y todos los deseos) desaparezcan para siempre?

title: The Final Book
description: The last book of Kelsey's favorite fantasy series goes missing from the library, so Craig decides to help her solve the mystery of who took it.

title: DC Super Hero Girls: Intergalactic Games
description: Super Hero High is facing off against Korugar Academy in the Intergalactic Games, but Lena Luthor takes advantage of the gathering of supers to enact her villainous plan.

title: Pesadilla de verano
description: Drago y los otros Bakugan de Los Fantásticos se enfrentan a una nueva y poderosa amenaza, solo para dejarlos preguntándose si todo habrá sido un sueño.

title: Starscream's Children Part 1
description: The Autobots received a distress call from the Nemesis and must come to the aid of their arch-enemies.

title: Una necesidad inquietante
description: La aparición de un nuevo campo Bakugan hace que los chicos del pueblo corran a buscar a sus propios Bakugan. Pero cuando el campo es contaminado, Lia debe salvarlos a todos.

title: #La dulce justicia - Cuarta parte
description: Cuando seis chicas comunes y corrientes descubren que cada una tiene un poder extraordinario diferente, deciden unir fuerzas para derrotar a algunos de los villanos más siniestros de Metrópolis en la parte 4 del episodio estreno.
originalseriesname: DC Super Hero Girls en Espanol

title: Fantasma, El Nino
description: Oscar y Erizo se hacen amigos de un fantasma que no recuerda quién es.

title: Trouble Helix
description: Flashback episode: Young Ben, Gwen, and Grandpa Max visit Azmuth on Galvan Prime. There, they have their first encounter with Malware, a corrupted Mechamorph who's determined to make Azmuth cure him, by any means!

title: Halloween vs. Christmas
description: When Santa tries to take over Halloween, it's up to the Titans and a few ghouls to stop him.

title: Birthday Blowout
description: Puppycorn's birthday wish is stolen by Master Frown, the biggest downer in the kingdom! To recover it, Unikitty and Puppycorn will have to venture into the most depressing land ever, Frown Town! Will they manage to recover the birthday wish from Frown before his wish (and all wishes) are wished away forever?

title: Wasteland
description: After Uncle Grandpa neglects his garbage duties, he embarks on a quest to save his friends from the overflowing pile of trash.

title: Bienvenidos al Inframundo Parte 2
description: Después de que Vic pierde una pelea de lucha libre, V&V viajan al inframundo para buscar el consejo de su tío, un famoso luchador llamado El Toro.

title: Heroes locales
description: Los Fantásticos provocan una ola de destrucción por accidente, y los padres de Dan se preguntan si deberían permitirle a los niños conservar sus Bakugan.

title: #SweetJustice Part 1
description: When six ordinary girls meet and discover that they each have extraordinary powers, they decide to join forces to take on one of Metropolis's most sinister villains.

title: Falafel's Fun Day
description: When Falafel decides to pack up and leave the city, Apple and Onion have to convince him to stay or they'll have to leave too.

title: Gwen O Ben
description: Cuando Ben interfiere con la misión de Hex -el mago malicioso- para los Titan Gloves, que hacen tareas de movimiento de tierra en un centro de trueque, Hex intercambia el cuerpo de Ben con el de Gwen, lo cual lo obliga a caminar un kilómetro y medio en sus zapatos iy viceversa!

title: Film Fest
description: It's opening night at the Unikingdom Film Festival! Everyone's excited to see what the friends made, particularly Richard, who considers himself the ultimate film expert and can't wait to blow everyone else's films out of the water with his own. But after playing the critic, will Rick's film be a masterpiece or a flop?

title: Receta Del Desastre
description: Durante el festival gastronómico Chefapalooza en las Montañas Rocosas, el Tri-Chefta, compuesto por tres cocineros famosos y villanos infames, persigue a Wildvine con la esperanza de crear el plato más exótico que jamás hayan preparado.

title: Cutting Corners
description: Ben approaches Geezer Bob about doing a little yard work to earn spending money, but when Ben goes Upgrade to transform the lawnmower into a super fast mowing machine, he accidentally draws the ire of Bob's gnome-neighbors, the tiny, terrifyingly tenacious Billy-Bob Goblins.

title: Primogenita
description: El Emperador Garmadon ha tomado el control de Ciudad Ninjago donde Lloyd se retira hacia las sombras. Mientras tanto, los otros Ninjas y Wu Joven quedan varados en el Reino de Oni y Dragón y descubren que no están solos.

title: Halloween
description: Raven tries to put the spirit of Halloween back in Halloween.

title: Jessica va al Arroyo
description: Cuando Craig y Jessica quedan encerrados fuera de la casa, Craig no tiene otra opción: debe llevar a su hermanita al Arroyo.
originalseriesname: Craig of the Creek en Espanol

title: No Me Ataques, Amigo
description: Ben y Billy Billones, su archienemigo, se enfrentan en un duelo por la supremacía en Laser Town, el parque de simulación de armas láser. Pero cuando, sin darse cuenta, Billy desata una rebelión robótica, y los lásers pasan de tocar a desintegrar, isu juego infantil se convierte en una guerra sin cuartel! Los enemigos descubren que deben dejar de lado sus diferencias y unirse para poder salir con vida...iy salvar al resto del planeta!

title: Scared Silly
description: When the Rust Bucket runs out of gas on a foggy East Coast road, Ben, Gwen and Max are forced to stay at a hotel being menaced by Creepy Carl, a local folklore expert, who may actually be a ghost!
